             were indicted for <rs id="t18250915-345-off1862" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18250915-345-off1862" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18250915-345-off1862" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18250915-345-victim1740" type="victimName">
                        Elizabeth 
                        Green
                     <interp inst="t18250915-345-victim1740" type="surname" value="Green"></interp>
