                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-345-off1862 t18250915-345-crimeloc1865"></join>, with intent to steal, and stealing therein, two pieces of crape, value 2 l.; four yards of calico, value 2 s.; a handkerchief, value 5 s.; two pairs of breeches, value 6 d.; two frocks, value 1 s.; two petticoats, value 1 s.; four yards of flannel, value 4 s.; a table-cloth, value 2 s.; eight napkins, value 3 s.; a tippet, value 2 d.; a purse, value 2 d.; four caps, value 1 s.; a pocket, value 4 d., and a half crown, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18250915-345-victim1741" type="victimName">
                        Maria 
                        short
                     <interp inst="t18250915-345-victim1741" type="surname" value="short"></interp>
